                    <span>I find the book to be very practical, and extremely helpful to entrepreneurs who are in the process of starting companies.  I highly recommend this book to first-time entrepreneurs...</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great book for entrepreneurs -- much more than law</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>9</span>
