                    <span>This book is an extremely helpful resource for anyone interested in establishing or working for a new business.<p>I made practical use of  several chapters within days of reading them.<p>Its easy-to-read style does  not compromise useful depth.<p>I highly recommend it to anybody starting,  thinking of starting, or considering working for a new enterprise.</span>
                  
              
